HEADWORD: Top-shell
<hw>Top"-shell`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of numerous species of marine top-shaped shells of the
genus <gen>Trochus</gen>, or family <fam>Trochidae</fam>.</def>⟦br⟧
